text: The A14 is a short autoroute (motorway) in France. It starts from the A13 and goes east towards Central Paris. The autoroute is about long. ==Exits and junctions== Junction number & name Westbound exits Eastbound exits 1 RN13, Pont de Neuilly, Puteaux, Suresnes RN13, Pont de Neuilly, Puteaux, Suresnes RN192, Boulevard de Mission Marchand, La Garenne-Colombes RN13, Avenue du Président Wilson, Rueil-Malmaison RN314, Route de Rouen, La Défense 5 Poissy A13, RN14, Poissy 6 Orgeval A13, RN13, Poissy, Orgeval A13, RN13, Poissy, Orgeval ==References== Category:Autoroutes in France
